---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import '../styles/components/inner-pages.css';

const meta = {
  title: 'Sound & Yoga | Shambala Holistic Retreat Centre | Fermanagh',
  description: 'Book sound baths, Chakra Dancing and weekly yoga classes in Enniskillen and Derrylin with Shambala, with gentle movement and meditation.',
  canonical: 'https://shambalaholisticandretreatcentre.com/sound-baths-yoga/'
};

const schema = {
  '@context': 'https://schema.org',
  '@type': 'Service',
  name: 'Sound Baths and Yoga in Fermanagh',
  serviceType: 'Sound bath, yoga and weekly yoga classes',
  provider: {
    '@type': 'HealthAndBeautyBusiness',
    name: 'Shambala Holistic & Retreat Centre'
  }
};
---

<BaseLayout {meta} {schema}>
  <section class="inner-hero inner-hero--sound">
    <div class="inner-hero__content">
      <p class="label">Sound Healing · Restorative Yoga · Meditation</p>
      <h1>Sound Baths and Yoga in Fermanagh</h1>
      <p>Immersive sound, gentle movement and deep rest at Shambala Holistic & Retreat Centre near Upper Lough Erne.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="page-section">
    <div class="split-layout">
      <div>
        <p class="label">Sound and Stillness</p>
        <h2>Let the Body Settle</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="copy-flow">
        <p>A sound bath is a meditative experience where you rest while resonant tones from instruments such as Tibetan bowls, crystal bowls and gong move through the room.</p>
        <p>At Shambala, sound baths may be offered as standalone sessions, as part of Slow Flow Rahanni Yoga evenings, during wellness days, or within residential retreats.</p>
        <p>The practice is simple: lie down, get comfortable, listen, and let the body move towards stillness.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="page-section page-section--mist">
    <div class="section-heading section-heading--simple">
      <p class="label">Sessions May Include</p>
      <h2>Sound, Breath and Gentle Movement</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="value-grid">
      <article>
        <h3>Sound Bath Meditation</h3>
        <p>Tibetan bowls, crystal bowls and gong tones create a calm field for deep relaxation.</p>
      </article>
      <article>
        <h3>Restorative Yoga</h3>
        <p>Slow, supportive yoga that helps the body soften before sound meditation.</p>
      </article>
      <article>
        <h3>Slow Flow Rahanni Yoga</h3>
        <p>A gentle evening practice that may be paired with sound bath meditation on selected dates.</p>
      </article>
      <article>
        <h3>Retreat Sound Baths</h3>
        <p>Many residential retreats include a sound bath as part of the evening programme.</p>
      </article>
      <article>
        <h3>Private Groups</h3>
        <p>Sound and yoga sessions can be discussed for small groups and wellbeing days.</p>
      </article>
      <article>
        <h3>First-Time Visitors</h3>
        <p>No experience is needed. Wear comfortable clothing and arrive ready to rest.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="page-section">
    <div class="section-heading">
      <div>
        <p class="label">Weekly Yoga · Enniskillen</p>
        <h2>Feel Relaxed, Centred and Balanced</h2>
      </div>
      <a class="btn btn-dark" href="https://wa.me/447713744589" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Message to Book</a>
    </div>

    <div class="split-layout">
      <div class="copy-flow">
        <p>Come stretch, breathe and unwind in a calm environment with weekly yoga classes connected with Shambala Holistic & Retreat Centre.</p>
        <p>Classes are suitable for all levels and for people who want gentle movement, a steadier breath and time to reset during the week.</p>
        <p><strong>Booking is essential.</strong> Enniskillen classes are £10 per session.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="class-schedule-grid" aria-label="Weekly yoga class schedule">
        <article>
          <p class="label">Mondays</p>
          <h3>5.30-6.30 pm</h3>
          <p>St. MacCartin's Cathedral Hall, Enniskillen.</p>
        </article>
        <article>
          <p class="label">Wednesdays</p>
          <h3>6-7 pm</h3>
          <p>Fermanagh House, Broadmeadow Place, Enniskillen.</p>
        </article>
        <article>
          <p class="label">Saturdays</p>
          <h3>9-10 am</h3>
          <p>Shambala Holistic & Retreat Centre, Derrylin. €10 per person.</p>
        </article>
        <article>
          <p class="label">By Request</p>
          <h3>Weekdays</h3>
          <p>Weekday yoga at Shambala Centre can be arranged by request. Booking essential.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="booking-strip" aria-label="Weekly yoga booking details">
      <div>
        <p class="label">Price</p>
        <strong>£10 / €10</strong>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="label">Booking</p>
        <strong>Essential</strong>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="label">Contact</p>
        <a href="https://wa.me/447713744589" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">+44 7713 744 589</a>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="label">Email</p>
        <a href="mailto:shambala108@icloud.com">shambala108@icloud.com</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="page-section page-section--mist">
    <div class="section-heading section-heading--simple">
      <p class="label">Regular Events</p>
      <h2>Chakra Dancing and Sound Bath Meditation</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="split-layout">
      <div class="copy-flow">
        <p>Chakra Dancing invites you to move gently and freely, helping you reconnect with your body, release tension, and flow through the energy of the chakras.</p>
        <p>Sound Bath Meditation lets the waves of sound wash over you as you listen to the gentle sounds of different melodious instruments. It is a deeply relaxing experience.</p>
        <p>There is an option to attend just the Chakra Dancing or Sound Bath separately.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="class-schedule-grid" aria-label="Chakra Dancing and Sound Bath Meditation schedule">
        <article>
          <p class="label">Schedule</p>
          <h3>Select Fridays</h3>
          <p>Dates to be confirmed with Shambala.</p>
        </article>
        <article>
          <p class="label">Format</p>
          <h3>Attend One or Both</h3>
          <p>Option to attend Chakra Dancing or Sound Bath Meditation separately.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="small-note">TODO: Confirm specific Friday dates with Sukhada before publishing dated listings.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="page-section page-cta">
    <div>
      <p class="label">Sound and Yoga Enquiry</p>
      <h2>Book a Sound Bath or Yoga Session</h2>
      <p>Contact Sukhada for weekly yoga classes, upcoming sound baths, yoga sessions and retreat availability.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="cta-actions">
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://wa.me/447713744589" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Message to Book</a>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost btn-ghost--inverse" href="mailto:shambala108@icloud.com?subject=Sound%20and%20Yoga%20Enquiry">Email Shambala</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
